00:48:17,977 --> 00:48:20,187
Hear me out later.

762
00:48:20,271 --> 00:48:22,690
Oh, sure. See you after work.

763
00:48:26,110 --> 00:48:29,614
What does Ms. Song have to do
with the sinkhole case?

